@host = http://localhost:5000

### Listar
GET {{host}}/orders

### Criar
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cliente": "Carlos Service",
  "valor": 99.90
}

### Listar de novo
GET {{host}}/orders

### Buscar por id válido
GET {{host}}/orders/1

### Buscar id inválido
GET {{host}}/orders/9999